REPOST 🔁 @riothealers 💜

REPRODUCTIVE HEALTH IS HEALTH.
So much has changed in our healthcare landscape since the overturning of Roe v Wade. In order to fight for reproductive justice to the best of our ability, we have to stay informed.

How? @connectrnapp has you covered.

By partnering with legal experts, nurses and community members, @connectrnapp created a specific toolkit, full of guidance and resources to help navigate the evolving healthcare landscape.

To access these exclusive resources, head over to @connectrnapp link in bio to learn more and sign-up.
